<ns1495:para xmlns:ns1495="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" xml:id="resources.information.technologies.java.j2ee.ejb.enterpriseBeans.entityBeans.introduction.introParagraph">

    Entity beans represent
    persistent business objects which exist accross client sessions and accross server crashes.
    They have a representation in a persistent storage technology like a relational or an
    object-oriented database.
